==English==

===Etymology===
From the city of Shergotty India, where the first specimen was found in 1865.

===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ˌʃɚ.gəˈtaɪt/

===Noun===
A type of meteorite composed of lava from a planet other than Earth.  See [http://geology.about.com/library/bl/images/blshergottite.htm geology.about.com article] for more information.

